com.invensense.casdk.client

Class CASDKUtilityActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • com.invensense.casdk.client.CASDKUtilityActivity

  • public class CASDKUtilityActivity
extends Activity
    This Activity represents second page of the application. It includes the fragmented layout to display rolling dice and values of different sensors that are present on CA-Board along with set of commands to test different features.
